oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: WCMI Barn Dance Review - 1937-02-dd - Part 3
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Broadcast of the WCMI Barn Dance Review, part 3 (based on the show being referred to as running from 8:00-8:45 and this 15 minute segment containing the closing theme). The collective performers have been assumed to be called the Kettle Kut-Up Gang based on writing on the disc. Featuring Juanita Moore, Accordion Annie, Cousin Elmer, Cicero, and Curley, with host Paul (last name unknown).
